Articles.Content:
Hello

 

I have a strange one. This so far affects just one probe in orbit around the Mun. I was given a contract to move it. It has been working as a com stalite and continues to do so. However when I took control I saw this

Now it still works as a sat but I have no control. What can be causing this?

I am running x64

Thanks for any help.

 

Edit : It gets worse just checked my probes around kerbin and they too have become an decoupler with a flame and puff of smoke. Corrupt save game? To many mods?
